article.guide
  .container-fluid
    .row
      .col-sm-3
        .box-max
          a(href="http://neo4j.com")
            img.img-responsive(src='images/neo4j-world.png')
          p.lead.text-center Guide Preview
      .col-sm-9
        .teaser.teaser-3
          h3 How-to
          p.lead Create a custom Neo4j Browser guide
          .icon-holder
            img.icon(src="images/learn-icon.png")
            ul.topic-bullets
              li Create content
              li Preview locally
              li Publish to server
            .clearfix
          button.btn.btn-cta(play-topic='how-to-guide') Learn how to create 

        .teaser.teaser-3
          h3 Library
          p.lead Curated collection of guides
          .icon-holder
            img.icon(src="images/books-icon.png")
            ul.topic-bullets
              li Cypher references
              li Domain examples
              li Modeling techniques
            .clearfix
          button.btn.btn-cta(play-topic='guide-library') Browse the library

        .teaser.teaser-3
          h3 What's this?
          p.lead A slightly modified Neo4j Browser
          .icon-holder
            img.icon(src="images/neo4j-icon.png")
            ul.topic-bullets
              li Static html+css+scripts
              li 
                a(href="http://www.browsersync.io") Browsersync
                |  host
              li No proxy for queries
            .clearfix

